tle>9月1號國家主席就割平民韮菜</title><updated>2025-08-19T14:56:57+08:00</updated><author><name>熊本肥熊</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T14:56:57+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573656083"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573656083"&gt;有貨快走轉投歐美&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011117&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T14:56:57+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5ad7251476808e87f7b5c3d94fedb76e</id><title>1177大行報告｜ 中生製藥獲野村調升目標價19%至9.17元 上調今明年收入及盈利預測</title><updated>2025-08-19T15:03:35+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T15:03:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573656148"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573656148"&gt;中生製藥&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG01177/?mtc=20048" target="_blank" uhash="02a4c0a4fb9dc02ba755ea4a79416ab4"&gt;（01177）&lt;/a&gt;上半年收入按年升10.7%，純利升12.3%. 野村發表報告指，中生製藥中期業績符預期，鑑於上調今明兩年的收入及盈利預測，將目標價由7.69元上調19.2%至9.17元，評級維持「買入」。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3995445/1177%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%EF%BD%9C%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%9F%E8%A3%BD%E8%97%A5%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E8%AA%BF%E5%8D%87%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E5%83%B919-%E8%87%B39.17%E5%85%83%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC" target="_blank" uhash="377ca861114218bbeb2ff9d80258a28c"&gt;1177大行報告｜ 中生製藥獲野村調升目標價19%至9.17元上調今明年收入及盈利預測&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011120&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T15:03:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5ef4f1bbcd80797ac0be21f6179a3830</id><title>新股IPO｜Shein據報考慮將基地遷回中國 冀助香港上市計劃獲批</title><updated>2025-08-19T15:06:29+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T15:06:29+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573656175"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573656175"&gt;Shein據報已考慮將基地遷回中國，冀以助北京當局批准在香港上市計劃。彭博引述知情人士表示，目前註冊於新加坡的快時尚電商平台Shein已就其在中國設立母公司事宜諮詢律師，據指目前討論尚處初步階段。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3995395/%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%EF%BD%9CShein%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%87%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%B7%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%80%E5%86%80%E5%8A%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9" target="_blank" uhash="8e3e89738563148802e59a8a2e5fbff3"&gt;新股IPO｜Shein據報考慮將基地遷回中國冀助香港上市計劃獲批&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011123&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T15:06:29+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>739175a0edcf08a00e693b8b9f3767e7</id><title>Hibor急升我好怕怕，人人沽貨掉渣渣。上證突破我笑哈哈，港股破頂我吹喇叭！</title><updated>2025-08-19T15:18:59+08:00</updated><author><name>富豪酒家</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T15:18:59+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="post