="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_41.gif"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.hk01.com/article/60268039?utm_source=01articlecopy&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral" target="_blank" uhash="7fb123a2d82451702eedc34463230c07"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/60268039?utm_source=01articlecopy&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011149&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T16:03:29+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>4a0e1164d7e4a66f9a0db5e6c33dba28</id><title>291業績｜華潤啤酒半年多賺23%創新高、績後曾拉升8% 中期息增逾24%至0.464元人幣</title><updated>2025-08-19T16:30:46+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T16:30:46+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573657047"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573657047"&gt;華潤啤酒&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://invest.hket.com/data/HKG00291/?mtc=20048" target="_blank" uhash="4fba1bbd4075fa48caf775a25a21edcc"&gt;（00291）&lt;/a&gt;上半年純利為57.9億元（人民幣，下同），按年升23%及創新高。潤啤擬派中期息每股0.464元，按年增長24.4%。華潤啤酒午後股價曾大升8%，高見28.66元，即市成交增至9億元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;期內，受益於啤酒業務高端化戰略的持續發展和原材料採購成本的節約，華潤啤酒綜合營業額239.4億元，按年升0.8%。毛利率上升2個百分點至創新高的48.9%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;飲酒人變多？&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="55" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_44.gif"&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3995485/291%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE%EF%BD%9C%E8%8F%AF%E6%BD%A4%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%9A%E8%B3%BA23-%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E3%80%81%E7%B8%BE%E5%BE%8C%E6%9B%BE%E6%8B%89%E5%8D%878-%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%E6%81%AF%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%BE24-%E8%87%B30.464%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3" target="_blank" uhash="37a5b11b45cacc01e71f42baaf3496b3"&gt;291業績｜華潤啤酒半年多賺23%創新高、績後曾拉升8%中期息增逾24%至0.464元人幣&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011163&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T16:30:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>730aac7a427a366aa5effca16c0d7b96</id><title>分析｜英特爾同樣是攤薄 為何特朗普及軟銀入股消息 股價卻一跌一升？</title><updated>2025-08-19T16:32:30+08:00</updated><author><name>katewells</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-19T16:32:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573657070"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573657070"&gt;Intel英特爾（美：INTC）股價在急跌3.7%後，盤後抽升5.2%，股價座過山車，波動的原因，是特朗普考慮換取英特爾10%股份，以及軟銀公布與英特爾的合作，投資20億美元，不過，兩者同是攤薄公司股權，為何股價卻一升一跌？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;以市場版報，英特爾因「芯片法案」獲得109億美元的撥款，包括直接商業製造與先進封裝專案補助約78.65億美元，涵蓋亞利桑那州、新墨西哥州、俄亥俄州與俄勒岡州多個重要產能擴充計畫，國防相關額外合約/補助30億美元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3995546/%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BD%9C%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E5%90%8C%E6%A8%A3%E6%98%AF%E6%94%A4%E8%96%84%E3%80%80%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%8F%8A%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E3%80%80%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%BB%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%87%EF%BC%9F" target="_blank" uhash="6dea3789c8586518387d06080ccd6c80"&gt;分析｜英特爾同樣是攤薄為何特朗普及軟銀入股消息股價卻一跌一升？&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://inews.hket.com/article/3995291/INTC%EF%BD%9C%E8%BB%9F%E9%8A%80%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E3%80%8C%E9%A3%9F%E9%A0%AD%E5%95%96%E6%B9%AF%E3%80%8D156%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E3%80%80Intel%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%BD%88%E5%8D%8A%E6%88%90" target="_blank" uhash="1d68c1974ebf5c8d1cc0f19168ffc844"&gt;INTC｜軟銀集團「食頭啖湯」156億元入股英特爾Intel股價盤後即彈半成&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32011165&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=196103736568a4372db49405_42310641"/><published>2025-08-19T16:32:30+08:00</published></entry></feed>